Test for sys_timer_restart:
===========================

this test checks that an error value is returned when trying to restart a timer that has not been started or initialized yet.

To use This Test:
1) install a blank kernel
2) use sos_tool to install /modules/unit_test/modules/kernel/timer_restart/no_init/no_init_test.mlf
3) run modules/unit_tests/modules/kernel/timer_restart/no_init/no_init_test.py

additional Function Dependencies:
